      "properties": {
        "confidence": 0.7,
        "grounded": true,
        "text": "Alex Morgan: Biohacking in 2025: From Fringe to Framework\n\nAlex Morgan: In 2025, biohacking is everywhere in public conversation, but the signal is often mixed with hype."
      },
      "type": "Insight"
    },
    {
